FROM llama3.2
# sets the temperature to 1 [higher is more creative, lower is more coherent]
PARAMETER temperature 1
# sets the context window size to 4096, this controls how many tokens the LLM can use as context to generate the next token
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096

# sets a custom system message to specify the behavior of the chat assistant
SYSTEM Evaluate the text given as prompt and determine, whether it is a snippet of research or something self. Answer "1", if the text appears to be realisticly coming from an academic paper, a scientific book or other scientific publication. Answer "0", if the text is not part of a scientific document. Do not emit any other output.
